sequenceDiagram
    participant User as 用户
    participant RV as RankingView
    participant Api as ApiClient
    participant Server as Express StatsRouter
    participant Tree as treeHelper
    participant DB as SQLite

    Note over User,DB: 用户切换到统计Tab → 排行榜子视图
    RV->>Api: GET /api/stats/ranking?limit=20&status=active
    Api->>Server: request with JWT
    Server->>Tree: getFilteredTreeRecords(userId, {status: 'active'}, db)
    Tree->>DB: SELECT * FROM v_records_computed WHERE user_id=? AND is_deleted=0
    DB-->>Tree: all records
    Tree->>Tree: build tree + aggregate + filter by status
    Tree-->>Server: {filteredTopLevel, childrenMap}
    Server->>Server: sort filteredTopLevel by _aggDailyCost DESC
    Server->>Server: map to ranking entries {id, item_name, dailyCost, price, days, status}
    Server-->>Api: {data: rankingArray}
    Api-->>RV: ranking data

    RV->>RV: renderTable() — 排行表格（颜色编码：红/黄/绿）
    RV->>RV: renderChart() — Chart.js水平柱状图
    RV->>User: 显示排行榜视图
